# GitHub workflow

All work uses [GitHub issues](https://github.com/Gitter499/cyclosim/issues) and pull requests.

## Branching

- **`dev`**: integration branch; open PRs here.
- **`main`**: stable releases; merge from `dev` via PR when a milestone batch is ready.
- Feature branches: `feat/issue-N-short-name` or `chore/...` from latest `dev`.

## Pull requests

- One milestone or focused change per PR.
- Title references the issue: `feat: M3b Cesium tile streaming (#7)`.
- Body includes `Closes #N` when the PR completes an issue.
- Granular commits on the branch; CI must pass before merge.

